    "Most of this data comes from publicly available internet sources, with a smaller portion consisting of preprocessed datasets and private data.",
    "While internet data contains positive and useful information, it also includes a significant amount of harmful and biased content.",
    "The expectation of tech companies and stakeholders is for AI models to be launched and monetized quickly.",
    "This is why the ChatGPT-3 model sometimes provides biased, inaccurate, or inappropriate responses.",
